---
title: Summery Chicken and Tomato Jam Bistro Sandwiches  with Roasted Parmesan Broccolini
description: This recipe is all about preserving the bounty of the season, which means making homemade tomato jam! Then, tender chicken is topped with creamy bocconcini and arugula, to showcase the best flavours of summer.
